title: Electricity prices for households in Denmark 2010 - 2019 , semi-annually
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Euro cents per kilowatt-hour. In total the number of data points it has is 19.
In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010_S2 and 2011_S1.
Maximum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, about 31.26 was reported at Year 2018_S1
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 26.7 was reached at Year 2010_S1
